1

00:00:00,000  -->  00:00:03,840
Along with the list methods we saw in the previous lesson,

2

00:00:03,840  -->  00:00:07,420
Python offers powerful functions to work with lists.

3

00:00:07,420  -->  00:00:11,460
In this video, we'll take a closer look at len and sorted.

4

00:00:11,460  -->  00:00:14,980
Len, as we just saw the length function,

5

00:00:14,980  -->  00:00:18,240
returns the number of elements in a list.

6

00:00:18,240  -->  00:00:22,425
This is a counter for finding the number of pieces in the collection.

7

00:00:22,425  -->  00:00:26,370
Sorted, on the other hand, returns a new list with the elements

8

00:00:26,370  -->  00:00:30,470
